values: I will be trying to go home for the next three weeks . . . I hope I will succeed but I doubt it.

How many times in your life you come across someone who embodies dignity and greatness and at the same time radiates profound humbleness because she remarkably understands her vulnerability? God's grace will be with you.
just trying to make you smile.
"It's a very short trip. While alive . . . live." Today i did not feel well. I did not go to work. A walk in the backyard helped a little.
Going to a conference in Canada. I hope it will not be that cold. See you when i come back.....take care.
